      <data key="d2">Cao.csv contains patient data for pancreatic cancer studies, including case identifiers, inclusion criteria, demographic details, tumor characteristics, pathologic staging, and follow-up information. Columns cover diagnosis, age, sex, race, tumor specifics, staging, medical history, cellularity fractions, and survival status.</data>
